n = int(input())
for i in range(n):
    m = list(map(int, input().split()))
    p = list(map(int, input().split()))
    lst1 = list(map(lambda a1, a2: a1 > a2, m, p))
    hihi = lst1.count(True)
    haha = lst1.count(False)
    if hihi > haha:
        print('A')
    else:
        print('B')

T = int(input())
for _ in range(T):
    (R1, W1, C1) = map(int, input().split())
    (R2, W2, C2) = map(int, input().split())
    A = (R1 > R2) + (W1 > W2) + (C1 > C2)
    B = 3 - A
    print('A') if A > B else print('B')

for _ in range(int(input())):
    (r1, w1, c1) = map(int, input().split())
    (r2, w2, c2) = map(int, input().split())
    ls = [r1, w1, c1, r2, w2, c2]
    a_points = sum([1 if ls[i] > ls[i + 3] else 0 for i in range(3)])
    b_points = sum([1 if ls[i + 3] > ls[i] else 0 for i in range(3)])
    print('A') if a_points > b_points else print('B')
